'''Rwanda ka Fasojamana''' ye jamana fitini ye ani jamana dasɔgɔlen min bɛ Dala Ba yɔrɔ la kɔrɔn-cɛma Afrika, a bɛ danbɔ ni [[Uganda]], [[Burundi]], [[Kongo ka Bɛjɛfanga Fasojamana]] ani [[Tanzania]] ye. A bɛ talikɛ mɔgɔ milion 10.1. Rwanda ye Afrika jamanaw lakoronen ye. Jamanaden fanba bɛ sɛnɛ matarafa. Tu jamana ani kulu dugukolo duman, fasojamana fitini bɛ wele « Kulu bankelen dugu » (Franse : Pays des Mille collines) [[Kinyarwanda]] n’o y’uka kan ye a bɛ fɔ (Igihugu cy’Imisozi Igihumbi).

Jamana in kera selekenani ɲɛjɔyɔrɔ ye Rwanda jahadi fagali senfɛ san 1994. Rwanda ɲinini boloda ka kɛ Forobanafolo tɔnden ye, latigɛ bɛna ta ka kɛɲɛ min ma san 2009.

